channel.title: Need help on RSMV
channel.description: So I looked at SilentCJ's tut on adding models to RSMV, I did everything, and I have like 100 models when I load RSMV. I've gone into main.java and went to server int. and it was at 554, so I press compile.bat and compiled, then I went to run.bat and started trying like 100 different things then it said accepted, then said Trying model: 654 accepted. Then it told me to close it. So I loaded RSMV and I have like 100 models.
